The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.

The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Ever had one of those days when you feel the need to workout but you're just too tired, or lazy, to get up and get moving? I'm sure we all have! 

That's why today's workout is just so perfect because this is a fat-burning exercise for when you need to burn those calories on your lazy days. It's highly efficient and it's the perfect workout to do when you're not in the mood to be active.
